'''''Rock-One''''' was the code name given to a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[miid ro'ik]] cruiser by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

''Rock-One'' entered the [[Dubrillion system/Legends|Dubrillion system]] shortly after the [[Battle of Helska IV]], where it was used as a base to launch [[Yorik-et|coralskipper]] probes against the surface of the world. Later ''Rock-One'' was targeted by Rogue Squadron during the evacuation of [[Dubrillion/Legends|Dubrillion]]; during the battle, it used [[Interdiction field/Legends|interdiction fields]] to prevent some of the convoy from heading to [[Agamar/Legends|Agamar]], necessitating their rerouting to [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]].

